        </ul>
    </h4>

    <h3 class="w-feature">Vous avez déjà un site</h3>
    <h5>
        Si vous avez déjà un site ou une page facebook, celui-ci peut aussi être référencé. 
    </h5>
    {{else}}
    <h1>As a Wine Event Organiser, what is your insterest to be registered?</h1>
    <h2 class="w-feature">What we offer</h2>
    <h4>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">A description of your wine event
                <ul class="list-group margin-inner-list">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Logo</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Edition</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Date</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Entrance fee, presale fee</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Place</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Flyer image</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Access Plan</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Opening hours</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Add event dates in google calendar, ical</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Contact (address, email, website, phone)</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Geolocalisation via google map</li>
