    <h2 class="w-feature">New functionalities are under development</h2>
    <h4>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li  class="list-group-item">Invitation and discount functionalities <span class="badge w-badge-info"> foreseen beginning 2020</span><br/><br/></li>
